channel.title: Need help getting compile to work
channel.description: I need help trying to get my compile to work.. whenever I try to compile it says [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: antilag/java Press any key to continue . . .[/code] Then my friend sent me his antilag and antilag.class, which his server has a perfectly working compile, and I get same error.. Then I tried taking out antilag, and I got this [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: client/java Press any key to continue . . .[/code] Same thing, with client/java instead of antilag/java.. can anyone help?
